msgid "It could be dangerous to topple these boxes over."
msgstr "この箱の山を倒すのは危険だ。"

msgid "A large pile of boxes that goes all the way to the ceiling."
msgstr "箱が天井まで積み上がっている。"

msgid "This room feels different..."
msgstr "この部屋は雰囲気が違うわね……"

msgid "Is it safe...?"
msgstr "安全なの……？"

msgid "Ah, there you are."
msgstr "ああ、来たか。"

msgid "Who are you...? What is this place?"
msgstr "あなたは……？　ここは一体何なの？"

msgid "Straight to the point I see."
msgstr "単刀直入だね。"

msgid "Well, this isn't quite your world."
msgstr "ここは、あなた達の世界では必ずしもない。"

msgid "...What?"
msgstr "……どういうこと？"

msgid "Let's not get into it. You're doing a ritual, correct?"
msgstr "深入りはやめよう。あなた達は儀式をしてる、そうだよね？"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Ending_K7_3.misc_ending.dlg.kat"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "Stop, and go home."
msgstr "儀式をやめて、家に帰りなさい。"

msgid "All of you. I mean it."
msgstr "全員。冗談じゃなく。"

msgid "Excuse me...?"
msgstr "何言ってるの……？"

msgid "Kat, if you keep doing what you're doing, things won't end well."
msgstr "キャット、このまま続けたら、良くない結末になる。"

msgid "Do you know this person, Kat?"
msgstr "ねぇキャット、あなたの知り合い？"

msgid "Not at all."
msgstr "いえ、全く知らないわ。"

msgid "They seem to know you, though."
msgstr "でも、向こうはあなたを知ってるみたいよ。"

msgid "What is it with everyone warning me lately?"
msgstr "どうして最近どいつもこいつも私に警告してくるわけ？"

msgid "I need some answers."
msgstr "答えなさい。"

msgid "So far, you haven't-"
msgstr "あなたはまだ――"

msgid "Stop! Don't cross that line."
msgstr "ストップ！　その線を超えないで。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Ending_K7_3.misc_ending.dlg.hoodie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "Sigh..."
msgstr "はぁ……"

msgid "If you haven't realized by now, the ritual works."
msgstr "まだ気づいてないようなら言うけど、儀式は成功する。"

msgid "It will take you somewhere you'll never return from."
msgstr "そしてあなたは、二度と帰ってこれない場所へ連れていかれる。"

msgid "If it works then... I should definitely finish it."
msgstr "成功するっていうなら……なおさら、絶対に最後までやるっきゃないわ。"

msgid "Kat, what are you saying...?"
msgstr "キャット、何言ってるの……？"

msgid "Sorry, but I can't listen to this person. I have my reasons for doing this."
msgstr "ごめん、でもこの人の言うことは聞けないわ。私には、やらなきゃいけない理由があるの。"

msgid "I don't know how much you value what you have right now but..."
msgstr "あなたが今の状況をどのくらい大事にしてるかは知らないけれど……"

msgid "If you continue down this path, you'll lose everything."
msgstr "この道を歩み続ければ、あなたは全てを失う。"

msgid "Everything you hold dear, and everything you don't."
msgstr "あなたが大切にしているものも、そうでないものも。"

msgid "Your questions will not receive any satisfying answers..."
msgstr "あなたの疑問には、満足のいく答えが得られないかもしれない……"

msgid "And everything you know about the world will turn meaningless."
msgstr "そして、あなたがこの世界について知っていることは、全て無意味になる。"

msgid "Those three."
msgstr "そこの3人。"

msgid "...?"
msgstr "……？"

msgid "Are you willing to sacrifice their lives for your so-called \"reasons\"?"
msgstr "あなたの「理由」とやらのために、あの子たちの命を犠牲にしてもいいの？"

msgid "Lives...?"
msgstr "命……？"

msgid "Furthermore, your own life."
msgstr "そして、あなた自身の命も。"

msgid "Are you willing to die for the answers you're seeking?"
msgstr "探している答えのために、あなたは命を落としてもいいの？"

msgid "Let's go back, Kat."
msgstr "引き返しましょう、キャット。"

msgid "I want to leave..."
msgstr "私も帰りたい……"

msgid "I don't believe you. Why don't you just give me my answers yourself then? Spare me the trip."
msgstr "信じないわ。なら、あなたが今ここで答えをくれてもいいでしょ？　手間を省いてよ。"

msgid "I thought so."
msgstr "だと思った。"

msgid "I've said what I needed to."
msgstr "言うべきことはもう言った。"

msgid "Why? Who are you?"
msgstr "どうして？　あなたは誰なの？"

msgid "Just someone who has seen too many humans die."
msgstr "私はただ、あまりに沢山の人の死を見てきただけ。"

msgid "It would sadden me to add you four to the pile."
msgstr "あなた達4人がそれに加わるのは、胸が痛い。"

msgid "Go home, Kat."
msgstr "帰りなさい、キャット。"

msgid "Can't you feel it in the air here? You're all in danger."
msgstr "ここの雰囲気からもわからない？　あなた達は今、全員危険にさらされてるの。"

msgid "Kat, please, this feels too dangerous..."
msgstr "キャット、お願い、危険すぎるよ……"

msgid "Kat, let's just go."
msgstr "キャット、いいから帰りましょう。"

msgid "Yeah, let's get out of here. I didn't sign up for this."
msgstr "そうよ、ここを出ましょう。こんな話は聞いてないわ。"

msgid "Kat, we don't want something bad to happen to you."
msgstr "キャットにひどい事が起こるのは、私たちも嫌だよ。"

msgid "Fine, let's go."
msgstr "いいわ、帰りましょう。"

msgid "Are you by any chance the same person from my dream earlier today?"
msgstr "あなたもしかして、今日の夢に出てきたのと同じ人？"

msgid "A dream...?"
msgstr "夢……？"

msgid "It must have been your subconscious warning you as well."
msgstr "それはきっと、あなたの無意識も、あなたに警告してたんだと思う。"

msgid "...I see."
msgstr "……なるほどね。"

msgid "(Oh.)"
msgstr "(そうだ。)"

msgid "(Should I give this person the blueprints I found...?)"
msgstr "(見つけた青写真をこの人に渡したほうがいいかな……？)"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "はい"

msgid "No"
msgstr "いいえ"

msgid "By the way..."
msgstr "ところで……"

msgid "I found these weird blueprints a few minutes ago."
msgstr "ついさっき、この変な青写真を見つけたの。"

msgid "Just take them."
msgstr "受け取って。"

msgid "Otherwise I might change my mind."
msgstr "さもないと、気が変わっちゃうかも。"

msgid "Huh... this is..."
msgstr "へえ……これは……"

msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "ありがとう。"

msgid "You're doing the right thing, Kat. Your father would be glad."
msgstr "キャット、あなたは正しい事をしてる。お父さんもきっと喜ぶよ。"

msgid "It's okay to accept the life you're left with. Don't destroy it."
msgstr "遺された人生を受け入れても良いんだよ。壊したりしないようにね。"

msgid "...I guess."
msgstr "……でしょうね。"

msgid "Kat!!!"
msgstr "キャット！！！"

msgid "Go already. You can't be here."
msgstr "さっさと行って。ここにいちゃ駄目。"

msgid "If what you said is true..."
msgstr "あなたの言ったことが本当なら……"

msgid "Then thanks."
msgstr "どうもありがとう。"

msgid "I'll pass on the ritual."
msgstr "儀式はやめておくわ。"

msgid "For tonight."
msgstr "今晩のところは。"

msgid "That's good enough."
msgstr "それだけでも充分。"

msgid "A large pile of trash cans. They all seem to be empty."
msgstr "ゴミ箱の大きな山。どれも空のようだ。"
